vista.time
Class DefaultTimeInterval

java.lang.Object
  vista.time.DefaultTimeInterval
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, TimeInterval
public class DefaultTimeInterval
extends java.lang.Object
implements TimeInterval, java.io.Serializable

A class encapsulating the interval associated with a time series. This can be represented by a string such as 1hour, 1min, 1hour_5min etcetra. This is meaningful really in the context of a regular time series.
